<resolution-body style="traditional" id="H211EB0FB78884E4C991D3259025172B2"> 
<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="HA78BC717173D4B76A27C596C9062CDD0"><text>That the following named Members be, and are hereby, elected to the following standing committees of the House of Representatives: </text> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Homeland Security: </header><text>Mr. LaLota (to rank immediately after Mr. Crane).</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Agriculture:</header><text>Mr. Valadao. </text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Natural Resources:</header><text>Mr. Downing. </text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure:</header><text>Mr. Yakym (to rank immediately after Mr. Ezell).</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Oversight and Government Reform:</header><text>Mr. McCormick. </text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Foreign Affairs:</header><text>Mr. Miller of Ohio. </text></committee-appointment-paragraph> </section> </resolution-body> <attestation><attestation-group><attestor display="no">Kevin F. McCumber,</attestor><role>Clerk.</role></attestation-group></attestation> </resolution> 

